long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: UrbaneBox is an online styling service that ships hand-selected outfits straight to your doorstep. Members get 10 days to try on the clothes before being charged and only pay for what they keep. There are no fees and free shipping. UrbaneBox also offers a monthly $60 membership, in which a curated package valued over $120 is arranged and shipped to your doorstep monthly. There are no obligations and you can skip or cancel anytime.
